SHAMELESS ( SEASON 8)
The eighth season of Shameless , an American comedy - drama television series based on the British series of the same name by Paul Abbott , was announced on December 19 , 2016 , a day after the seventh season finale .
The season , which premiered on November 5 , 2017 , consisted of a total of 12 episodes .
This is also the last season to feature Isidora Goreshter as series regular , as she announced her departure from the series following the season finale .
